Package: mcanalysis
Title: Menstrual Cycle Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Kyra", "Delray", email = "kyra.delray@wolfson.ox.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Analyze the effect of menstrual cycle phase on outcomes using
    Generalized Additive Models (GAM). Takes period dates and outcome data,
    processes cycles, normalizes outcomes to individual means, fits GAM models,
    identifies inflection points, and produces publication-ready visualizations.
